data.description:
New Offering 3bedrm + Office or 4th bedrm. and for NEW ROOF to be installed.  Move in condition with updated Appliances, flooring, Garage screen enclosure. PROP LAYOUT UNDER CLIP shows Measurements.
This great room also has a screened porch across the rear of home. Recently painted and ready for new owner. This offering INCLUDES the 3 lots on Begonia, with home in the middle, so plenty of room on each side with 240 x 125.  This is an area near schools and shopping both in Bayside Lakes and the Malabar Road areas, with some of the area roads having been newly paved for the growth of new residences, many with the larger homesite.  No HOA to restrict you.
This is a metal frame home and as pictured, includes storm shutters and room for pool.
